
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Sensitivity of grassland carbon pools to plant diversity, elevated CO2, and soil nitrogen addition over 19 years
AU  - Pastore, Melissa A.
AU  - Hobbie, Sarah E.
AU  - Reich, Peter B.
Y1  - 2021/04/27
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/04/27
N1  - doi: 10.1073/pnas.2016965118
DO  - 10.1073/pnas.2016965118
T2  - Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences
JF  - Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences
JO  - Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences
SP  - e2016965118
VL  - 118
